00:05:56.410 --> 00:05:57.260
Kekal.

00:05:57.260 --> 00:05:58.680
Aku, Sang Abadi, akan memberitahumu,

00:05:59.390 --> 00:06:01.270
dekrit kekaisaran akan tiba hari ini.

00:06:01.550 --> 00:06:03.530
Anda dapat menuju Chang'an secara terbuka.

00:06:04.690 --> 00:06:05.670
Apa maksudmu?

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:07.840
Anda…

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:11.040
akan menjadi Kaisar.

00:06:15.390 --> 00:06:16.390
Aku?

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:17.560
Tepat.

00:06:17.750 --> 00:06:18.590
Anda.

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:22.600
Ketika Anda menjadi Kaisar dan berada di Chang'an,

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:25.720
Tentu saja kamu bisa merebut kembali Qilin.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:36.230
Aku pernah mendengar Duke of Guangling

00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:37.770
(Penasihat Wang Bingji;
Menteri Liu De)

00:06:37.770 --> 00:06:39.120
